INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (97,0,'Bimat (With Brush) 3 ml. (0.03%)','bimat-with-brush','Drops','bimat-500x500-1-copy-1-min-170046819729.png','0','<p><strong>Usage:</strong></p>\n\n<p>When using Bimat 3ml, it is crucial to follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions carefully and read the medication label thoroughly. Use the prescribed dosage and do not exceed or decrease it without medical guidance. Administer the medication directly into the affected eye(s) as directed by your healthcare provider.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Bimat 3ml offers several positive benefits in the treatment of glaucoma:</p>\n\n<p>Lowering intraocular pressure: The primary goal of Bimat 3ml is to reduce the elevated pressure inside the eye. By doing so, it helps to prevent further damage to the optic nerve and maintains the health of your vision.</p>\n\n<p>Effective glaucoma management: Bimat 3ml has been proven to be highly effective in controlling intraocular pressure, which is essential for managing glaucoma. By consistently using this medication, you can help preserve your vision and slow down the progression of the disease.</p>\n\n<p>Convenient and easy to use: Bimat 3ml comes in a user-friendly packaging with a precise applicator, making it easy to administer the medication accurately. The convenient size and design allow for hassle-free application, ensuring that you can incorporate it into your daily routine effortlessly.</p>\n\n<p>Long-lasting effects: Bimat 3ml provides sustained pressure-lowering effects, reducing the need for frequent administration throughout the day. This allows for greater convenience and compliance with the treatment regimen, enhancing the overall effectiveness of managing glaucoma.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Precautions:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Before using Bimat 3ml, it is important to consider the following precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Inform your healthcare provider: Ensure that you inform your doctor about any existing medical conditions or allergies you