ase the risk of priapism should use Kamagra 100mg tablets with caution.</li>\n	<li>If you experience any side effects while taking Kamagra 100mg Tablet, such as chest pain, vision changes, or hearing loss, seek immediate medical attention.<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>','<p>Kamagra Chewable is a chewable tablet that is taken orally and contains 100mg of Sildenafil Citrate, the active ingredient that helps men who have difficulty getting and maintaining erections.</p>\n\n<p>Erectile dysfunction is caused by insufficient blood flow to the penis. Kamagra works by increasing blood flow during sexual stimulation. When sexually stimulated, nitric oxide is released in the erectile tissues of the penis. This chemical activates an enzyme called guanylate cyclase, which increases the levels of cyclic guanosine monophosphate (cGMP), another chemical responsible for blood vessel relaxation, allowing more blood flow to erectile tissues to create an erection. Phosphodiesterase type 5 (PDE5) is also present and breaks down cGMP, leading to a loss of erection due to the prevention of blood flow. Kamagra inhibits the action of PDE5 specifically, allowing the activation of cGMP to create an erection.</p>','<p><strong>Side Effects:</strong></p>\n\n<p>The majority of side effects do not necessitate medical attention and usually subside as your body becomes accustomed to the medication. However, if they persist or cause concern, it is recommended to consult your doctor.</p>\n\n<p>The common side effects are listed below:</p>\n\n<p>Headache</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Stiffness</li>\n	<li>Nosebleeds</li>\n	<li>Blurred vision</li>\n	<li>Indigestion</li>\n</ul>','[\"kamagra-100-soft-chewebale-min-170125026860.png\"]','KAM0100',1,'1','2023-11-29 09:31:28','2023-12-30 06:37:42'),(114,0,'Acamprol 333mg','acamprol-333mg','Tablet','acamprol-333mg-11-171404166182.webp','ACA0333','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>It is best to take Acamprol Tablets with food. Only after quitting drinking alcohol totally will it work. Take