 your medical history with your healthcare professional, especially if you have a history of heart problems, kidney problems, or any other significant medical conditions. Aprecap 125/80 may require caution or dose adjustments in such cases.</p>','<p>A prescription drug called Aprecap 125/80 Capsule is used to alleviate nausea or vomiting that occurs as a side effect of chemotherapy or anti-cancer treatment. It prevents the brain from receiving the signal that triggers nausea and vomiting</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<p>The majority of adverse effects are temporary and go away as your body becomes used to the medication. If they persist or you&#39;re concerned about them, speak with your doctor.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Constipation</li>\n	<li>Indigestion</li>\n	<li>Headache</li>\n	<li>Tiredness</li>\n	<li>Loss of appetite</li>\n	<li>Hiccup</li>\n</ul>','[\"aprecap-125mg-80mg-17028814884.webp\"]','APR0125',1,'0','2023-12-18 06:38:17','2025-07-25 11:07:18'),(139,0,'Arimidex 1mg','arimidex-1mg','Tablets','arimidex-1mg-170288167496.webp','ARI001','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>To ensure the best results, it is important to follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions and read the medication label carefully. Take Arimidex orally, usually once a day, with or without food. It is advisable to take the medication at the same time each day for consistency. If you have any questions or concerns about the dosage or usage, consult your healthcare provider.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Breast cancer treatment: Arimidex 1mg has demonstrated effectiveness in treating hormone receptor-positive breast cancer. By reducing estrogen levels, it helps inhibit the growth of certain types of breast tumors, preventing their progression and reducing the risk of recurrence.</p>\n\n<p>Improved survival rates: Studies have shown that Arimidex, when used as an adjuvant therapy in postmenopausal women with early-stage breast cancer, has led to increased overall survival rates and a decreased risk of cancer recurrence compared to other treatments.</p>\n\n<p>Minimized side effects: Compared to other hormonal therapies, Arimidex has been found to have a favorable side effect profile. It is associated with a lower incidence of certain side effects commonly associated with tamoxifen, such as blood clots and endometrial cancer. By reducing the levels of estrogen in the body more selectively, Arimidex helps minimize the impact of estrogen-related side effects.</p>\n\n<p>Convenience and compliance: Arimidex is available in a convenient once-daily oral formulation, making it easy to incorporate into a daily routine. Its simplified dosing schedule can enhance patient compliance and ensure the medication is taken as prescribed for optimal results.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Before starting Arimidex treatment, it is crucial to inform your healthcare provider about any pre-existing medical conditions, allergies, or medications you are taking. This information will help your doctor determine if Arimidex is appropriate for you and if any adjustments are needed.</p>','<p>Arimidex 1mg, also known by its generic name Anastrozole 1mg, is a medication that offers numerous benefits for individuals dealing with certain types of breast cancer. It belongs to a class of drugs called aromatase inhibitors, which work by reducing the levels of estrogen in the body. Arimidex is primarily prescribed to postmenopausal women with hormone receptor-positive breast cancer, but it may also be used in specific cases for other conditions under medical supervision.</p>','<p>Side Effects:</p>\n\n<p>While Arimidex is generally well-tolerated, some individuals may experience side effects. It&rsquo;s important to remember that not everyone will experience these side effects, and they are often temporary. Common side effects may include:</p>\n\n<p>Joint pain or stiffness: Some patients may experience mild to moderate joint discomfort while taking Arimidex. This can usually be managed with over-the-counter pain relievers or other strategies recommended by your healthcare provider.</p>\n\n<p>Hot flashes: Similar to other hormonal therapies, Arimidex can cause hot flashes or feelings of warmth. These are typically temporary and may decrease over time.</p>\n\n<p>Fatigue: Some individuals may experience mild fatigue or tiredness while taking Arimidex. It is important to prioritize rest and self-care during this time.</p>','[\"arimidex-1mg-170288167496.webp\"]','ARI001',1,'0','2023-12-18 06:41:27','2025-07-25 11:07:20'),(140,0,'Aromasin 25mg','aromasin-25mg-','Tablets','aromasin-25mg-170288191482.jpg','ARO025','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>To ensure optimal results, it is recommended to follow the instructions provided by your healthcare provider or pharmacist when taking this medication. It is important to read and adhere to all the instructions on the medication label. By using the medication as directed, you can maximize its effectiveness and safety.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Breast Cancer Treatment: Aromasin 25mg is highly effective in treating hormone receptor-positive breast cancer in postmenopausal women. It works by reducing the production of estrogen in the body, which helps to slow down or stop the growth of cancer cells.</p>\n\n<p>Adjuvant Therapy: Aromasin 25mg can be used as adjuvant therapy, meaning it is administered after primary treatment like surgery or radiation, to further decrease the risk of cancer recurrence. It plays a vital role In preventing the return of breast cancer in postmenopausal women.</p>\n\n<p>Hormone Therapy: Aromasin 25mg is an important component of hormone therapy for breast cancer. It helps to suppress estrogen production, which is essential because estrogen can promote the growth of certain breast cancers. By blocking the conversion of androgens into estrogen, Aromasin 25mg helps to maintain a low estrogen level in the body.</p>\n\n<p>Well-Tolerated: Aromasin 25mg is generally well-tolerated by most patients. It offers a valuable treatment optio