h it. Meningitis is an inflammation of the lining of the brain, endocarditis is an infection of the lining of the heart and its valves.</p>\n\n<p>Take the CAMPICILLIN 250MG CAPSULE on an empty stomach. Even if you feel better in the middle of the therapy, it is crucial to take CAMPICILLIN 250MG CAPSULE for the whole term recommended by your doctor to get the best effects. Inadequate infection control may come from not following the therapy&#39;s full course or skipping doses between therapies.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Vomiting</li>\n	<li>Nausea</li>\n	<li>Diarrhea</li>\n	<li>Skin rash</li>\n	<li>Itching</li>\n</ul>','[\"campicilin-250-mg-170723971771.webp\"]','CA250',1,'0','2024-02-06 17:15:29','2025-08-06 05:24:06'),(221,0,'Campicilin 500 mg','campicilin-500-mg','Capsule','campicilin-500-mg-170723983297.webp','CA500','<p>How to use:</p>\n\n<p>Take CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET on an empty stomach at least 30 minutes before or 2 hours after eating to prevent stomach problems.With a glass of water, completely chew the CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET. Never crush, break, or chew it. Shake the bottle thoroughly before using to ensure suspension. The measuring cup included in the package should be used to administer it orally.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>A broad-spectrum penicillin antibiotic, CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET is effective against a variety of bacterial illnesses. You can get sick from harmful or contagious bacteria, and they can proliferate swiftly in your body. The major effects of CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET are the killing of germs and the prevention of bacterial infection growth. Meningitis, kidney infections, gonorrhea, pneumonia, and infections of the intestines or stomach are among the bacterial infections that are treated with it. The combination is known as co-fluampicil and is made up of CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET and the penicillin antibiotic flucloxacillin.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Allergies: If you have a known allergy to penicillin or any other cephalosporin antibiotics, inform your doctor before taking Campicilin 250 mg. Allergic reactions can range from mild rashes to severe anaphylaxis, which is a life-threatening condition.</p>\n\n<p>Medical History: Share your complete medical history with your healthcare provider, especially if you have a history of kidney disease, liver disease, or any gastrointestinal disorders. This information will help your doctor determine the appropriate dosage and duration of treatment.</p>\n\n<p>Drug Interactions: Notify your doctor about all the medications, herbal supplements, and over-the-counter drugs you are currently taking. Certain medications can interact with Campicilin 250 mg and affect its efficacy or increase the risk of side effects.</p>','<p>The drug CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET is a member of the penicillin antibiotics drug class. Many bacterial infections of the lungs, skin, stomach, and kidneys as well as sexually transmitted diseases like gonorrhea are often treated with CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET. When dangerous bacteria enter the body, reproduce, and spread infection, a bacterial infection results. Any region of the body might become infected, and it multiplies very quickly.</p>\n\n<p>Ampicillin, which is effective against several types of bacteria, is present in CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET. It prevents the formation of the bacterial cell wall, which is necessary for its survival. CAMPICILLIN 500MG TABLET destroys germs as a result and stops the spread of bacterial infection.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Nausea</li>\n	<li>Vomiting</li>\n	<li>Stomach pain</li>\n	<li>Diarrhoea</li>\n	<li>Vaginal itching or discharge</li>\n</ul>','[\"campicilin-500-mg-170723983297.webp\"]','CA500',1,'0','2024-02-06 17:17:21','2025-08-06 05:24:18'),(222,0,'Candesartan  8mg','candesartan-8mg','Tablet','candesartan-8mg-170724001871.jpg','CA08','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>Follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions carefully when taking Candesartan 8mg. Make sure to read and follow all the directions on the medication label. It is important to take the medication regularly and at the same time each day to achieve the best results. Do not stop taking Candesartan without consulting your doctor, even if you start feeling better.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Candesartan 8mg offers several benefits for individuals with hypertension and other cardiovascular conditions. These include:</p>\n\n<p>Blood pressure management: Candesartan effectively lowers high blood pressure, reducing the strain on the heart and blood vessels. By keeping blood pressure within a healthy range, it helps to prevent complications such as heart attacks, strokes, and kidney problems.</p>\n\n<p>Cardiovascular protection: Candesartan has been shown to have protective effects on the heart and blood vessels. It helps to reduce the risk of cardiovascular events and improves overall cardiovascular health.</p>\n\n<p>Kidney protection: Candesartan can also provide kidney protection, especially for individuals with diabetes or kidney disease. It helps to prevent or slow down the progression of kidney damage, which is a common complication of these conditions.</p>\n\n<p>Tolerability and convenience: Candesartan is generally well-tolerated and has a low incidence of side effects compared to some other antihypertensive medications. Its once-daily dosing regimen adds to its convenience and ease of use.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Before starting Candesartan 8mg, it is important to discuss your medical history and any other medications you are taking with your healthcare provider. They should be aware of any allergies or previous adverse reactions you may have had to Candesartan or other similar medications. Inform them about any existing medical conditions, including liver or kidney problems, heart disease, or diabetes.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>Candesartan 8mg is a medication that is commonly prescribed to treat various cardiovascular conditions. It belongs to a class of drugs called angiotensin II receptor blockers (ARBs) and is primarily used to manage high blood pressure (hypertension). Candesartan helps to relax and widen the blood vessels, allowing for smoother blood flow and lowering blood pressure.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Here is some important information about Candesartan 8mg:</p>','<p>Side Effects:</p>\n\n<p>Most people taking Candesartan 8mg do not experience significant side effects. However, it is essential to be aware of possible adverse reactions. If you do experience any side effects, they are generally mild and transient. Some common side effects may include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Dizziness</li>\n	<li>Fatigue or tiredness</li>\n	<li>Headache</li>\n	<li>Back pain</li>\n	<li>Nausea or stomach discomfort</li>\n</ul>','[\"candesartan-8mg-170724001871.jpg\"]','CA08',1,'0','2024-02-06 17:20:27','2025-08-06 05:24:27'),(223,0,'Candesartan 32mg','candesartan-32mg','tablet','candesartan-tab-32mg-170724025016.jpg','CA32','<p>Uasge:</p>\n\n<p>It is important to follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions and take Candesartan 32mg exactly as prescribed. Read and adhere to all the instructions on the medication label. Take the tablet orally with or without food, preferably at the same time each day. It is important to maintain a consistent schedule to ensure the medication&rsquo;s effectiveness.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Effective blood pressure control: Candesartan 32mg is highly effective in managing high blood pressure, which is a common health condition that can lead to serious complications such as heart disease, stroke, and kidney problems. By lowering blood pressure, Candesartan helps to reduce the strain on the heart and blood vessels, promoting overall cardiovascular health.</p>\n\n<p>Cardiovascular protection: Candesartan has been shown to have additional benefits beyond blood pressure reduction. It helps to protect the heart and blood vessels from damage caused by high blood pressure, reducing