</li>\n</ul>','[\"ciplox-ointment-5-gm-170801537414.jpg\"]','CI005',1,'0','2024-02-15 16:43:01','2025-09-17 09:21:14'),(257,0,'Ciplox TZ 500 mg 600 mg','ciplox-tz-500-mg-600-mg','tablet','ciplox-tz-500-mg-600-mg-170801541711.jpg','CI600','<p>How to use:</p>\n\n<p>The dosage and duration of Ciplox-TZ Tablet 10&#39;s should be followed, as prescribed by your doctor. To get the best results, it is suggested that you take it with food and at a certain time. You might occasionally feel sick to your stomach, throw up, lose your appetite, get a headache, etc. Most of these Ciplox-TZ Tablet 10 adverse effects subside over time without the need for medical intervention. However, contact your doctor if the adverse effects continue to bother you. Please contact your doctor right away if you suffer any adverse reaction symptoms, including rashes, itching, swelling, shortness of breath, etc.</p>\n\n<p>Ciplox-TZ Tablets, 10 should only be taken as directed by a physician. Always follow your doctor&#39;s instructions exactly when taking Ciplox-TZ Tablet 10s. Based on your medical condition, your doctor will give you advice on how frequently to take your pills. Ciplox-TZ Tablet 10 should be taken with a full glass of water.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>The 10 Ciplox-TZ Tablets contain both the antibiotics ciprofloxacin and tinidazole. The antibiotic ciprofloxacin stops bacterial cells from dividing. Additionally, it prevents bacterial cells from healing. The death of the bacterium results from both of these events. Tinidazole eliminates anaerobic bacteria and parasites that cause illnesses. Their DNA is harmed in order to work.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Bacterial Infection Treatment: Ciplox-TZ Tablet is primarily prescribed for the treatment of various bacterial infections, including urinary tract infections, gastrointestinal infections, respiratory tract infections, skin and soft tissue infections, and sexually transmitted infections. Ciprofloxacin, one of the active ingredients, is a broad-spectrum antibiotic that helps eliminate the bacteria causing the infection.</p>\n\n<p>Parasitic Infection Treatment: Ciplox-TZ Tablet is also effective against certain parasitic infections, such as giardiasis and amoebiasis. Tinidazole, the other active ingredient, is an antiprotozoal agent that helps eliminate the parasites responsible for these infections.</p>\n\n<p>Combination Therapy: The combination of ciprofloxacin and tinidazole in Ciplox-TZ Tablet provides a comprehensive approach to treating both bacterial and parasitic infections simultaneously. This can lead to more effective eradication of the causative organisms and a faster resolution of symptoms.</p>\n\n<p>Broad Spectrum of Activity: Ciplox-TZ Tablet has a broad spectrum of activity against a wide range of bacteria and parasites. This makes it a versatile option for the treatment of various infections caused by susceptible organisms.</p>\n\n<p>Convenient and Easy to Take: Ciplox-TZ Tablet is available in tablet form, which makes it convenient and easy to take orally. The tablets are usually swallowed whole with water, and the prescribed dosage and duration of treatment should be followed as directed by the healthcare provider.</p>\n\n<p>Reduction of Symptoms: By targeting the underlying cause of the infection, Ciplox-TZ Tablet helps alleviate symptoms such as fever, pain, inflammation, diarrhea, and discomfort associated with bacterial and parasitic infections.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>A combination drug called Ciplox-TZ Tablet 10 is primarily used to treat a wide range of illnesses brought on by anaerobes, protozoa, susceptible Gram-positive and Gram-negative organisms. Gram-positive organisms are responsible for inflammatory diseases such as skin infections, pneumonia (infection characterized by inflammation of the air sacs in one or both lungs), endocarditis (infection of the inner lining of the heart chamber and heart valves), septic arthritis (inflammatory arthritis brought o