on. However, if you are concerned or if the side effects persist, it is recommended that you consult your doctor.</p>\n\n<p>The most common side effects are listed below:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Nausea</li>\n	<li>Vomiting</li>\n	<li>Indigestion</li>\n	<li>Dryness in mouth</li>\n	<li>Headache</li>\n</ul>','[\"dazeagra-50-30mg-170825557743.jpg\"]','DA50',1,'0','2024-02-18 11:27:32','2025-09-17 11:46:46'),(283,0,'Demelan Cream 20gm','demelan-cream-20gm','Cream','demelan-cream-20gm-170825584456.jpg','DE20','<p>How to use:</p>\n\n<p>According to your doctor&#39;s instructions, demelan cream should be used to the affected area, especially at night. Apply Demelan cream with a gentle massage on a surface of healthy skin that is free from wounds and sores. Wash your hands before and after using Demelan cream unless your hands are the area that has to be treated.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Reduction of hyperpigmentation: Demelan cream works by inhibiting the production of melanin, the pigment responsible for skin color. It can help reduce the appearance of hyperpigmentation, including dark spots, age spots, and sunspots, resulting in a more even skin tone.</p>\n\n<p>Treatment of melasma: Melasma is a common skin condition characterized by brown patches or uneven pigmentation on the face. Demelan cream can be effective in lightening these patches and reducing the severity of melasma.</p>\n\n<p>Brighter complexion: Regular use of Demelan Cream can help improve the overall brightness and radiance of the skin. It can help restore a youthful and glowing complexion by reducing the appearance of dullness and uneven skin tone.</p>\n\n<p>Exfoliation and skin renewal: Demelan Cream contains glycolic acid, which acts as an exfoliant, helping to remove dead skin cells and promoting the growth of new, healthy skin cells. This can result in smoother, softer, and more rejuvenated skin.</p>\n\n<p>Fade acne scars: Demelan cream may also help fade acne scars and post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation. It can promote skin healing and reduce the appearance of acne-related discolorations, leading to a clearer and more uniform complexion.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Patch test: Before applying Demelan Cream to larger areas of the skin, it is recommended to perform a patch test on a small area to check for any adverse reactions or skin sensitivity.</p>\n\n<p>Avoid sensitive areas: Take care to avoid applying Demelan Cream near the eyes, mouth, or other sensitive areas of the face. If accidental contact occurs, rinse thoroughly with water.</p>\n\n<p>Sun protection: Demelan cream can increase the skin&#39;s sensitivity to sunlight. It is crucial to protect your skin from excessive sun exposure by using sunscreen, wearing protective clothing, and avoiding prolonged sun exposure.</p>\n\n<p>Avoid other skin irritants: Avoid using other harsh or irritating skincare products, such as scrubs or exfoliants, while using Demelan Cream, as it may increase the risk of skin irritation.</p>','<p>Demelan cream is a topical medication used to treat skin pigmentation issues. Arbutin, glycolic acid, and kojic acid dipalmitate are its primary components. It helps to lessen dark skin discoloration brought on by the sun, some illnesses, pregnancy, and other circumstances. Demelan cream is a skin-lightening product that enhances the skin&#39;s tone and texture. Only the skin should receive demelan cream application. Avoid using this cream more often than recommended because doing so could irritate your skin.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Skin irritation (redness, itching, burning)</li>\n	<li>Dryness and peeling of the skin</li>\n	<li>Increased sensitivity to sunlight</li>\n	<li>Rare cases of allergic reactions (rash, itching, swelling)</li>\n</ul>','[\"demelan-cream-20gm-170825584456.jpg\"]','DE20',1,'0','2024-02-18 11:30:56','2025-09-17 11:47:21'),(284,0,'Deplatt 75mg','deplatt-75mg','tablet','deplatt-75mg-170825590442.jpg','DE75','<p>How to use:</p>\n\n<p>Based on your 