umed while using DESLOR 5MG TABLET.</p>\n\n<p>When administered to patients with impaired kidney function, KIDNEY DESLOR 5MG TABLET should be used with caution. Therefore, before using it, talk to your doctor.</p>\n\n<p>ALLERGY</p>\n\n<p>If you have a loratadine or desloratadine allergy, do not take DESLOR 5MG TABLET.</p>','<p>Desloratadine serves as the active component of the anti-allergic drug Deslor 5mg Tablet. It is an anti-allergic medication, thus it is regarded comfortable to use because it doesn&#39;t make you tired. This medication aids you by relieving allergy symptoms like runny nose, sneezing, red, itchy eyes, hives, and skin rashes (food allergy, dust allergy, etc.). The mechanism by which this medication functions is to prevent the release of the chemical that causes allergic reactions. Before beginning to take this medication, let your doctor know about all other prescription, over-the-counter, and herbal medications you are taking.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<p>The majority of side effects do not necessitate medical attention and typically subside as your body adapts to the medication. However, if they persist or if you have concerns about them, it is advisable to consult your doctor.</p>\n\n<p>The common side effects are listed below:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Sleepiness</li>\n	<li>Dizziness</li>\n</ul>','[\"deslor-5mg-170825606425.jpg\"]','DE005',1,'0','2024-02-18 11:34:33','2025-09-17 11:48:29'),(286,0,'Desogestrel Tab  75mcg','desogestrel-tab-75mcg','tablet','desogestrel-tab-75mcg-170825620283.jpg','DE75','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>To ensure optimal results, it is recommended to follow the instructions provided by your healthcare provider or pharmacist when taking Desogestrel Tab. It is important to read and adhere to all the instructions on the medication label. By using the medication as directed, you can maximize its effectiveness and safety.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Highly effective contraception: Desogestrel Tab 75mcg is a reliable contraceptive 