hieve and maintain a firm and long-lasting erection.</p>\n\n<p>Management of rapid ejaculation: In addition to treating impotence, Extra Super P Force also contains dapoxetine, which is specifically designed to address rapid ejaculation. Dapoxetine works by increasing the time it takes for ejaculation to occur, helping men have better control over their ejaculation and prolonging sensual activity.</p>\n\n<p>Enhanced sensual performance: Extra Super P Force not only addresses impotence and rapid ejaculation individually but also provides a comprehensive solution for both conditions simultaneously. By improving erectile function and prolonging ejaculation, this medication can significantly enhance overall sensual performance and satisfaction.</p>\n\n<p>Convenience and cost-effectiveness: Combining sildenafil citrate and dapoxetine into a single medication eliminates the need to take two separate pills, making it more convenient for individuals experiencing both impotence and rapid ejaculation. Additionally, using a combination medication can be more cost-effective compared to purchasing two separate drugs.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>Before taking Extra Super P Force, it is crucial to consult with your healthcare provider or pharmacist to ensure it is safe for you. Inform them about any pre-existing medical conditions, ongoing treatments, or medications you are currently taking to avoid potential interactions or complications. It is also important to disclose any known allergies to medications or other substances.</p>','<p>Extra Super P Force is a medication that combines two active ingredients, sildenafil citrate and dapoxetine. It is primarily used to treat two common male sensual disorders: impotence (ED) and rapid ejaculation (PE). This unique combination medication offers several benefits to individuals experiencing these conditions.</p>','<p>Side Effects:</p>\n\n<p>Like any medication, Extra Super P Force may cause some side effects. However, it is essential to note that not everyone experiences them, and most side effects are temporary and mild. Common side effects associated with Extra Super P Force may include headache, dizziness, nausea, flushing, nasal congestion, and indigestion. These side effects are generally well-tolerated and resolve on their own as your body adjusts to the medication.</p>\n\n<p>Remember to consult your doctor or pharmacist if you have any concerns or questions regarding Extra Super P Force or its potential side effects. They can provide personalized advice and guidance based on your specific health circumstances.</p>','[\"extra-super-p-force-170832435530.jpg\"]','EXP',1,'0','2024-02-19 06:32:44','2025-05-26 09:46:19'),(337,0,'Eyemist E/D 10 ml','eyemist-e/d-10-ml','Drops','eyemist-e-d-10-ml-170832441624.jpg','EY010','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>When using Eyemist E/D 10 ml, it is important to follow the instructions provided by your doctor or healthcare professional. Read and comply with all the directions on the packaging for optimal use. If you have any concerns or questions, consult your healthcare provider.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Dry Eye Relief: Eyemist E/D 10 ml is specifically formulated to provide relief for individuals suffering from dry eyes. It helps to lubricate and moisten the eyes, reducing discomfort and irritation caused by dryness.</p>\n\n<p>Long-Lasting Hydration: The solution in Eyemist E/D 10 ml is designed to provide long-lasting hydration to the eyes. It helps restore and maintain the natural moisture balance of the eyes, ensuring a soothing and comfortable feeling.</p>\n\n<p>Clear Vision: By hydrating the eyes, Eyemist E/D 10 ml promotes clear vision. It can help alleviate symptoms such as blurred vision or sensitivity to light that may be associated with dry eyes.</p>\n\n<p>Convenient and Easy to Use: Eyemist E/D 10 ml comes in a user-friendly bottle that allows for easy application. Its compact size makes it convenient to carry, ensuring you can provide quick relief 