 have ever had a kidney, heart, or lung transplant, kidney disease, a joint or tendon disorder such as rheumatoid arthritis (an autoimmune disorder that causes pain, swelling, and loss of function in the joints), seizures (fits), epilepsy, or if you engage in regular physical activity. Taking Levoflox 250 Tablet 10s may exacerbate myasthenia gravis (a disorder of the nervous system that causes muscle weakness) and lead to severe difficulty breathing or fatality. Avoid dairy products while taking Levoflox 250 Tablet 10&#39;s. Additionally, sunlight exposure should be avoided while taking Levoflox 250 Tablet 10&#39;s, as it may increase phototoxicity or photosensitivity. Before taking Levoflox 250 Tablet 10s, patients with epilepsy and irregular heartbeat (QT prolongation) must inform their doctor.</p>','<p>Levoflox 250 Tablet 10&#39;s is a fluoroquinolone antibiotic belonging to the third generation. Antibiotic that is highly effective against a variety of microorganisms. Levoflox 250 Tablet 10&#39;s is used to treat a variety of bacterial infections, including acute pneumonia, bronchitis, cutaneous infections, and urinary tract infections. A bacterial infection is a condition in which bacteria multiply and induce an infection within the body. It can target any part of the body and multiply rapidly.</p>\n\n<p>Dangerous bacteria can cause illness and rapidly replicate in the body. Toxins are chemicals produced by pathogenic bacteria that can damage tissue and induce illness. Levoflox 250 Tablet 10 binds to the enzymes (Topoisomerase IV and DNA gyrase) responsible for the division of bacteria and halts the process of bacterial proliferation, thereby killing bacteria.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Nausea</li>\n	<li>Vomiting</li>\n	<li>Diarrhoea</li>\n	<li>Constipation</li>\n	<li>Indigestion</li>\n	<li>Trouble sleeping</li>\n</ul>','[\"levoflox-250mg-170948225420.jpg\"]','LE250',1,'1','2024-03-03 16:13:21','2025-10-08 05:18:08'),(438,0,'Levoflox 500mg','levofl