worse and even result in death. It is best to stay away from dairy products and Oflox TZ Tablet 10s.</p>','<p>A combination of medications known as &quot;antibiotics&quot; called Oflox TZ Tablet 10 is primarily used to treat various illnesses brought on by bacteria and protozoans. Oflox TZ Tablet 10&#39;s are used to treat a wide range of infections brought on by anaerobes, protozoa, Gram-positive and Gram-negative bacteria that are sensitive. Malaria and dysentery, which produce colon inflammation, are two instances of infections brought on by protozoa.</p>\n\n<p>Ofloxacin and tinidazole are two antibiotics that are combined to form the Oflox TZ Tablet 10s. Numerous bacterial illnesses can be treated and prevented with the aid of ofloxacin. It has a bactericidal character, which means that it kills the bacteria that cause infections in order to function. It blocks the action of bacterial cells, finally wiping off the bacteria and stopping the infection from spreading. A broad-spectrum antibiotic, Oflox TZ Tablet 10&#39;s are effective against most Gram-negative bacteria, many Gram-positive bacteria, and certain anaerobes (bacteria that do not require oxygen to survive). Tinidazole, on the other hand, eliminates the anaerobic bacteria and parasites that cause illnesses. Their DNA is damaged in order for it to work.</p>','<p>Side effects:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Nausea</li>\n	<li>Vomiting</li>\n	<li>Headache</li>\n	<li>Headache</li>\n	<li>Metallic taste</li>\n	<li>Stomach pain</li>\n	<li>Loss of appetite</li>\n</ul>','[\"oflox-tz-600-mg-200-mg-171150985397.jpg\"]','OF600',1,'0','2024-03-27 03:25:16','2025-10-08 05:42:17'),(520,0,'Olmecip 20mg','olmecip-20mg','tablet','olmecip-20mg-171151014610.jpg','OL20','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>It is crucial to follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions and take Olmecip 20 mg exactly as prescribed. Read the medication label and any accompanying patient information leaflet thoroughly. Take the medication orally, usually once a day, with or witho