ork.</p>','<p>Prasita common side effects</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bleeding</li>\n</ul>','[\"prasita-10-mg-17115584498.webp\"]','PR0',1,'0','2024-03-27 16:54:21','2025-10-08 05:47:01'),(560,0,'Pravastatin Tab 20mg','pravastatin-tab-20mg','tablet','pravastatin-tab-20mg-171155856969.jpg','PR20','<p>Usage:</p>\n\n<p>Follow your doctor&rsquo;s instructions and read the medication label carefully before taking Pravastatin 20mg. Take the medication as directed and avoid taking more or less than the prescribed dose. It is usually taken once daily, with or without food. If you have any questions or concerns about the dosage or usage, consult your doctor or pharmacist.</p>\n\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n\n<p>Pravastatin 20mg offers several benefits in promoting heart health and managing cholesterol levels:</p>\n\n<p>Cholesterol management: Pravastatin is highly effective in reducing LDL (low-density lipoprotein) cholesterol, often referred to as &ldquo;bad&rdquo; cholesterol. Lowering LDL cholesterol levels can help prevent the buildup of plaque in the arteries, reducing the risk of heart disease, heart attacks, and strokes.</p>\n\n<p>Cardiovascular risk reduction: By lowering cholesterol levels, Pravastatin 20mg can significantly reduce the risk of cardiovascular events in individuals who have a history of heart disease or are at high risk due to other factors such as diabetes or smoking.</p>\n\n<p>Maintenance of healthy blood vessels: Pravastatin has been shown to improve the function of the endothelium, the inner lining of blood vessels, promoting their health and reducing inflammation.</p>\n\n<p>Positive impact on overall health: By reducing cholesterol levels and maintaining cardiovascular health, Pravastatin 20mg can contribute to an overall improvement in health and well-being, allowing individuals to lead an active and fulfilling life.</p>\n\n<p>Precautions:</p>\n\n<p>It&rsquo;s important to discuss your medical history and any existing health conditions with your 