r men who require moderate-strength support in managing ED. Its long-lasting effect, often extending up to <strong>36 hours</strong>, gives users flexibility and spontaneity in intimate moments, often earning it the nickname &ldquo;the weekend pill.&rdquo;</p>','<h3><strong>Possible Side Effects</strong></h3>\n\n<p>While <strong>Tadarise 20</strong> is generally well-tolerated, some individuals may experience side effects such as:</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p>Headache</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Back pain</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Muscle aches</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Nasal congestion</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Indigestion or flushing</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Dizziness or mild vision changes</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>These effects are usually temporary and subside on their own. However, if symptoms persist or if you experience chest pain, shortness of breath, or a prolonged erection lasting more than 4 hours, seek immediate medical attention.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3><strong>Precautions and Safety Guidelines</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p>Do not use if allergic to Tadalafil or similar medications</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Not recommended for individuals taking nitrates for chest pain</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Inform your healthcare provider of any heart, liver, or kidney conditions</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Use with caution in older adults or those with blood pressure issues</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Keep the medicine out of reach of children and store in a cool, dry place</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>','[\"screenshot-2025-07-22-093627-175315720231.png\"]','TA20',1,'1','2025-07-22 04:07:58','2025-07-22 04:07:58'),(778,0,'Vidalista  20mg','vidalista-20mg','Tablets','screenshot-2025-07-22-100440-175315889067.png','VI20','<h3><strong>Key Benefits of Vidalista 20mg</strong></h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p>Improves blood flow to the penis for better erection quality</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p>Provides up to <strong>36 hours</strong> of effectiveness, earning it the title of &ldquo;weekend pill&rdquo;</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>